g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0b408824fe4f83340af3de0f5fec5c809e3c32","tid":2248711,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d77b8d10fbcc08f28d7e09dfe335934e87e9cbfd","tid":2248711,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T21:16:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555439-20201019.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555439-20201019.htm&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=65b1f904\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555439-20201019.htm&h=1186757e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555439-20201019.htm</a><br />\n蓬佩奧：將制裁向伊朗售武的個人或實體<br />\n<br />\n聯合國對伊朗的武器禁運已於周日終止，伊朗可以從其他國家購入坦克、戰機等軍備提升軍力。伊朗外交部說，不會大舉採購武器。外長扎里夫說，伊朗與世界的國防合作正常化，是多邊主義及區域和平與安全的勝利。美國國務卿蓬佩奧說，華府準備利用國內機構，制裁向伊朗供應、出售或轉讓常規武器的個人或實體；而提供技術培訓、財務支持和服務的個人或實體， 也會受到制裁。<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-19 04:59:48"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T00:48:52.000Z","msg":"美國向聯合國宣戰~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0cd2bc1f5d4038bc4b82b58b089fd92f9b362b","tid":2248711,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T01:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}